      "title": "Ranil will be sworn in as Acting President tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe will be sworn in as the Acting President tomorrow (15th) morning. With the resignation of President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa, Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe is scheduled to be sworn in as the Acting Prime Minister tomorrow."
      ],
